This is libptpt2

This library is under developement yet, but example software is able to
download images.

Download  and instal libusb (libusb.sf.net).
To compile libptp and example program type make.
After that run ./dx3500 vendorID ProductID.

You can obtain vendor and product id by dmesg:
for example:

Product: KODAK DX3500 Digital Camera
usb.c: unhandled interfaces on device
usb.c: USB device 65 (vend/prod 0x40a/0x500) is not claimed by any active driver

to download pictures type:
./dx3500 0x40a 0x500
